DISCRETIONARY APPEALS ALLOWED

95-2468. State v. Weber.

Franklin County, Nos. 95APC05-534, 95APC05-545 and 95APC06-717. On motion to consolidate case with 95-1377 and 95-1466, State v. Gustafson, Mahoning County, No. 94 C.A. 232. Sua sponte, cause held for the decision in 95-1377 and 95-1466; briefing schedule stayed.

Stratton, J., not participating.
